{"id":4027,"date":"2019-01-30T14:35:04","date_gmt":"2019-01-30T14:35:04","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=4027"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:47:23","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:47:23","slug":"hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-phong-cach-noi-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-phong-cach-noi-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trong Phong c\u00e1ch N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Trong phong c\u00e1ch N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4n b\u1eadt c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i, h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea9n gi\u1ea5u. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0m n\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. M\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0 \u201c\u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nh\u1eefng \u00f4 c\u1eeda l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebb vinh quang l\u1ed9ng l\u1eaby khi \u00e1nh d\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e9t xu\u1ed1ng, t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh; ho\u1eb7c khai th\u00e1c \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng qua v\u00e1ch k\u00ednh, h\u1ec7 r\u00e8m, khe l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed5i b\u1eebng sinh kh\u00ed cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3971\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Thiet-Ke-Phong-Khach-Hien-Dai-Byzan09-reduce.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Thiet-Ke-Phong-Khach-Hien-Dai-Byzan09-reduce.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-cont